Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  喂喂  老媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是我  虎侍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天提早下班了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.94,0:00:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  收到了  裙帶菜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  我打算最近回家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃什麼？都好啦  什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？A種B種的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親味道的晚宴套餐？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑臭老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上哪有向回家的兒子索要伙食費的父母啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不管你怎麼做理所當然都是母親味道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我老媽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.99,0:00:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且晚宴套餐不就是剩下的晚飯嗎！你當我不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.07,0:00:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  竟然掛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那臭老太婆心情一不好就馬上掛電話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.71,0:00:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才不太想回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第9話\N小次郎和命運的分歧點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.07,0:02:36.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看了沒？深夜的  BAMBOO…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.92,0:02:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.81,0:03:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部團活動已經開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護面之類的  也要拿出來曬做什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長套已經很破舊了吧…要換了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件制服  是同間學校的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露餡的話怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露餡了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:46.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個  哪一個更靈驗一些呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.23,0:04:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我想兩個都有效
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼兩個我都要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:09.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的惠顧  歡迎下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添同學  麻煩你把這些擺放在店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來看看情況  來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也有點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.49,0:04:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  看你做得蠻起勁的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,習慣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  也是很好的社會實踐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  選什麼樣的比較好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  不問我為什麼在這裡挑選商品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,營業動力  營業動力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.69,0:04:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上啊  我打算這次放假的時候回一趟老家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老媽一大把年齡了淨喜歡這樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以打算買點什麼當作禮物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是你媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老太婆的房間真就像這種店裡的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本讓人想不到是50多歲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:13.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給老媽這太貴！我去換別的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先回學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您的惠顧  歡迎下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  說話口氣要高興點快樂點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情也要跟著變啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎下次再來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  多去部團露下臉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我果然還是贏不過勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  段君  給你水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃部長  讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  段他怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  榮花他的確變強了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  果然是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.51,0:06:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有劍道的素質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還和外行人沒什麼兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻能抓住我行動的破綻  採取我難以擊中的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他的天質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然現在還毫無持久力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今後一定會突飛猛進的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在畢業前我能不被超過就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎？讓那種角色變強
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係…那種角色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都  你亂打一通是沒法擊中的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃！好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖  不怕不怕不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  校園暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對小都都做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都！你用刺擊還太早了！想殺人啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外行人不准用！危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過天質不差啦  努力練習的話小都都也能變強哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小都都！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.55,0:08:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起幹勁來了呢  真期待這次的大賽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今天就到這裡  明天再…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.99,0:08:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  已經結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？打工那邊呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛結束  我想稍微再參加一下部團活動…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微休息一下  再繼續練習吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  看你上氣不接下氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  口渴了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.38,0:08:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這混雜著青春汗水中的芬芳的醬油香味…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  都忘了已經過三分鐘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在道場吃泡麵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒吃午飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙帶菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你放太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.82,0:09:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  珠姬是為了我而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著去擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收禮物的時候要怎麼說好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要裝作若無其事地而且要表現最大限度的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.52,0:09:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.31,0:09:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣太普通了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您生日…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  珠姬打工真得很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  那孩子太溫柔  也許不想讓我知道打工的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:52.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝您…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你珠姬！我打心裡深愛著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不行不行  不管怎麼說這太肉麻了  肉麻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興啊  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變成一個好孩子爸爸太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也照這樣子純真地  腳踏實地地  美麗地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健壯的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:20.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吧！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.84,0:10:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘  小手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.37,0:10:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是「伸手」啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（劍道的篭手（こて）與訓狗用口令お手（おて）的諧音…）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你保重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:46.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.95,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來家裡沒酒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.46,0:11:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我正要停的車位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.96,0:11:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  但是先搶先得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼  那臭老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也買些泡麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡麵和咖喱  還有罐頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是平民的好朋友啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是畫裡面單身漢會買的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  啤酒在哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.31,0:11:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩一箱了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！那是我正想拿走的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  但是先搶先得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:13.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這算什麼！不是擺明瞭硬搶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去買旁邊的不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的不是啤酒很貴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買一箱你也太囂張了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是個沒正當職業的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:27.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買零散的足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是沒正當職業的！我有正式的工作！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒  這個該死的老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在收銀台只開一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.86,0:12:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想繞過我搶在前面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  看那個分量…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他搶先的話我就要浪費很多時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:12:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想得逞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  蕎麥麵你要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你賠我！賠我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人  我馬上取新的給您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我閉嘴  是這傢伙不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…這個錢我來出…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！錢由我來出
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就出給你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧…什麼都別想了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種吃父母的Neet族還有臉開什麼車！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是Neet！也不是沒正當職業的！我是高中教師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教師！少騙人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.12,0:15:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那邊室江高中的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.81,0:15:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做石田虎侍！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田虎侍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是…這樣  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  石田老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？和平常一樣咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:43.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就是很好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數學不行  怎麼樣都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最用功的說卻不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.71,0:15:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然文系不怎麼用功也能過關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:55.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺越來越討厭  不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在玩弄我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.57,0:16:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有這自覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.97,0:16:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀梨乃  教我數學啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行  儘管來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  說回來紀梨乃你有什麼不擅長的科目嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.11,0:16:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就這樣都比我高對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家到齊了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然老師還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始練擺振吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  段郎  給你毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真體貼呢  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.59,0:16:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡…歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想榮花果然是個了不起的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.46,0:16:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺振的力道越來越強了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:16:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會變強的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  榮花同學會變強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.98,0:17:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是能毫不猶豫地進攻的人  沒有多餘動作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是能變強的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  宮崎同學也會變強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.99,0:17:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠你累了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小珠累了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:21.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你打工真的很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.02,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在老師來之前去休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.16,0:17:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠在老師來之前休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.56,0:17:32.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都因為是一年級所以很輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.47,0:17:33.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.05,0:17:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段君不管上了二年級三年級還是這麼悠哉哉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.54,0:17:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊  小鞘前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  不能欺負後輩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:53.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你這全年級前二十的優等生給我閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.66,0:17:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  在說期中考試嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小都都也很慘對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  段郎是優等生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.41,0:18:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全年級390人中排名第二！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第四
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是贏不了段君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過老師還真慢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲到的話實在太不像話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.83,0:18:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老…老師你什麼時候…？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來好像要消失了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的可能會消失也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能在這學校待不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校長他說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教到這個學年度結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:56.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那老師不就成了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無業
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.73,0:19:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼校長突然這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是校長而是理事長命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.95,0:19:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼理事長會親自下命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在超市和一個老太婆吵了一架…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說那個老太婆是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:22.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長是個男人  非常溫柔敦厚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理事長的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是理事長夫人說了我的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那麼那夫人就是超市的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:30.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老太婆？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  也不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那老太婆到底是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事長的近鄰  和理事長夫人關係超好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.39,0:19:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而理事長好像很怕老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  大家帶好護具
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從切返開始練習咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你們也稍微擔心一下我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是被學校開除了  也就不能當顧問了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算我們擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:04.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有用不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:05.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.66,0:20:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家可以去求校長不要辭退我之類…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不打算做什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…像我這種沒什麼成就的年輕人就算說什麼也沒用…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  那我們就從現在開始取得成就不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.16,0:20:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們劍道部越來越強
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後進軍全國大賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.65,0:20:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要留下好結果  誰都無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.61,0:20:38.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  全國大賽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:44.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果劍道部拿到成績的話  也許我就能繼續待下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.36,0:20:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒時間了  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.66,0:20:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有拼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.28,0:20:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…有你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有川添珠姬！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:20:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的珠姬是無敵的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.81,0:21:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於老師則是無職的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒被開除！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！拼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室江高中劍道部的新目標就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出賽全國大賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是同等的好成績！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.95,0:21:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  練習開始！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我自己！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天打工就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力到最後哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始連招呼都打不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.45,0:21:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原來是拂塵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:45.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:27.94,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.33,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:55.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:02.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:10.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:17.63,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:25.63,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:32.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:40.47,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:48.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.24,0:22:22.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:27.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:34.33,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.36,0:22:55.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:02.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.29,0:23:10.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.90,0:23:17.63,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:20.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:25.63,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:32.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:35.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:40.47,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:48.15,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hi Honey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:24:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到毫不迷茫的紳士榮花段十郎\N朝氣蓬勃的帥哥簡稱DanDanDan的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:11.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（這是果汁）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給在這種時間還在惡作劇的小貓咪們送上一句話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戀愛的鍔迫中退後的一方就是敗者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.32,0:24:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  夠帥
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.11,0:24:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回是「宮崎都的憂鬱和初次大賽」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.41,0:24:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會讓你變得憂鬱的！小都都！
